312
00:30:08,915 --> 00:30:10,915
Jadi banyak perdamaian.

313
00:30:13,454 --> 00:30:15,454
Tahukah kau mengapa aku
banyak menulis "Ping An"?

314
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,160
Sebuah nama.

315
00:30:38,690 --> 00:30:40,690
Dengar...

316
00:30:41,404 --> 00:30:43,404
